{"id": 59551, "date": "2025-09-06T04:00:13", "date_gmt": "2025-09-06T11:00:13", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59551"}, "modified": "2026-06-01T19:26:26", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-02T02:26:26", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-6-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/06/kingdom-of-days-september-6-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 6"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill rehearses for their upcoming and destined-for-legend Clearwater Swim Club show with fill-in drummer Dave Hazlett covering for Vini, who is stuck in Richmond due to a legal misunderstanding.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29225\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1970-09-06-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1970-09-06.jpg?fit=201%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"201,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1970-09-06\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1970-09-06.jpg?fit=201%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29225 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1970-09-06.jpg?resize=201%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"201\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1970-09-06.jpg?w=201&amp;ssl=1 201w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/202