560669&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-09-06b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?fit=710%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20916 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?resize=758%2C1093&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1093\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?w=1141&amp;ssl=1 1141w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?resize=208%2C300&amp;ssl=1 208w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?resize=710%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 710w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?resize=768%2C1108&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06b.jpg?resize=1065%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1065w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20917\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-09-06c/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?fit=1939%2C1494&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1939,1494\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598560724&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-09-06c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?fit=758%2C584&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20917 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?resize=758%2C584&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"584\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?w=1939&amp;ssl=1 1939w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?resize=300%2C231&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?resize=1024%2C789&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?resize=768%2C592&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2003-09-06c.jpg?resize=1536%2C1183&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2016:\u00a0</strong>Gearing up for publicity surrounding the release of\u00a0<em>Born to Run</em> (the book), Bruce tours Freehold with a CBS film crew and sits down for an interview at his home. The footage will air later in the month (look for it in our September 18th installment).</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PHXN2FFEuJU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. In attendance tonight: former first lady Michelle Obama.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12585\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-09-06/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/2018-09-06.jpg?fit=339%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"339,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;\\u00a9 Felipe Ramales / SplashNews.co&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-09-06\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/2018-09-06.jpg?fit=339%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12585 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/2018-09-06.jpg?resize=339%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/2018-09-06.jpg?w=339&amp;ssl=1 339w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/2018-09-06.jpg?resize=203%2C300&amp;ssl=1 203w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce reveals he has peptic ulcer disease, and under the advice of his doctor he announces the postponement of his remaining 2023 tour dates.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54317\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/asbury_park_press_2023_09_08_a1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Asbury_Park_Press_2023_09_08_A1-scaled.jpg?fit=882%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"882,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Asbury_Park_Press_2023_09_08_A1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Asbury_Park_Press_2023_09_08_A1-scaled.jpg?fit=353%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-54317\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Asbury_Park_Press_2023_09_08_A1.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2025:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins an array of all-star panelists at the Bruce Springsteen Archives and Center for American Music&#8217;s 50th Anniversary Symposium for\u00a0<em>Born to Run</em>. He also performs &#8220;Born to Run&#8221; and &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; with E Streeters past and present to close the show.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"69429\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/06/kingdom-of-days-september-6-2/asbury_park_press_2025_09_09_a2/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Asbury_Park_Press_2025_09_09_A2-scaled.jpg?fit=2060%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2060,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&q